## Conclusion

This technical stack specification provides the blueprint for implementing the Political Social Media Analysis Platform. The hybrid database approach combined with APIFY actors for data collection offers an optimal balance of relational integrity, document flexibility, and vector search capabilities to support all the features defined in the PRD.

